Invalid Filenames Dialog Box

Requires: Base Development System

Select Tools»LLB Manager, select a directory or a VI in an LLB, and select File»Check Filenames to display this dialog box.

Use this dialog box to check filenames for portability to other platforms.

This dialog box includes the following components:

  • Filenames not valid on all platforms—Displays the files with names that are not useable on other platforms.
